Hi Fred,

Well, technically you're correct, but you didn't simplify it as far as
you could.  Since multiplication is commutative (order doesn't matter), 

  14ab + 21ba = 14ab + 21ab

              = (14 + 21)ab

              = 35ab

Does this make sense? 

